DAWEN = Solana Web3 ecosystem

Core:
- Trading (real data only)
- Social (DAWEN Pulse)
- Gaming (skill-based, on-chain)
- Dawen City (Habbo-style inside Gaming)

RULES

Blockchain:
- Solana only
- Non-custodial
- Wallet = user identity
- activeWallet = single source

RPC:
- use process.env.SOLANA_RPC_URL
- never default Solana RPC
- no hardcoded keys

Trading:
- real price, mcap, liquidity, volume
- no fake data

Chart:
- one chart only
- no refresh / no flashing
- update last point only
- default = MCAP

Data:
- selectedToken.mint = source
- chart = price = mcap = holders

Social:
- posts, likes, comments, replies, reposts
- follow + messages
- profile (username, avatar, bio)
- data updates everywhere

Gaming:
- skill-based only (no gambling)
- real crypto rewards (Solana)

Dawen City:
- inside Gaming
- avatars, rooms, real-time interaction
- NFT items possible

Token:
- assets = activeWallet.publicKey
- holders = selectedToken.mint

Data rules:
- no duplicates
- no mixed sources
- always synced

Storage:
- Supabase storage
- public URLs only
- no blob

Security:
- public read
- write = owner only
- do not break features

Important:
- do not break working features
- no fake data
- behave like real trading app